===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[στέφανος]]''' (''stefanos'') "that which surrounds or encompasses, a crown, wreath, chaplet", from  '''[[στέφω]]''' (''stefo'') "to put round, to surround".

===Proper noun===
